org.deeplearning4j.models.sequencevectors.graph.walkers.impl

Class WeightedWalker<T extends SequenceElement>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.deeplearning4j.models.sequencevectors.graph.walkers.impl.RandomWalker<T>
      • org.deeplearning4j.models.sequencevectors.graph.walkers.impl.WeightedWalker<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GraphWalker<T>

    public class WeightedWalker<T extends SequenceElement>
extends RandomWalker<T>
implements GraphWalker<T>
    This is vertex weight-based walker for SequenceVectors-based DeepWalk implementation. Instead of random walks, this walker produces walks based on weight of the edges.
